{"title":"BlackHeart Bike Co. Has a New Custom Cerakote Program","link":"https://bikerumor.com/blackheart-bike-co-has-a-new-custom-cerakote-program/","date":1697558358000,"content":"<p><img width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/BlackHeart-Bike-Co.-Custom-Serakote-paint-program-bronze.jpeg\" alt=\"BlackHeart Bike Co. Custom Serakote paint program bronze\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/BlackHeart-Bike-Co.-Custom-Serakote-paint-program-bronze.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/BlackHeart-Bike-Co.-Custom-Serakote-paint-program-bronze-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/BlackHeart-Bike-Co.-Custom-Serakote-paint-program-bronze-800x533.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/BlackHeart-Bike-Co.-Custom-Serakote-paint-program-bronze-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/BlackHeart-Bike-Co.-Custom-Serakote-paint-program-bronze-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/BlackHeart-Bike-Co.-Custom-Serakote-paint-program-bronze-720x480.jpeg 720w\" /></p>\n<p>Located in the small, mountain town of Truckee, California BlackHeart Bike Co. has announced that they are introducing a custom paint program using the durable Cerakote coating. Cerakote is an ultra-thin, highly-durable, heat-cured ceramic coating. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Customers will be able to select from the 241 H-Series colors for the following applications: </p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Road Ti – Fork color</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Allroad Ti – Fork color</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Allroad AL/Alt – Frame, Fork, and Logo colors</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/BlackHeart-Bike-Co.-Custom-Serakote-paint-program-custom-color-fork-e1697209843997.jpeg\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"733\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/BlackHeart-Bike-Co.-Custom-Serakote-paint-program-custom-color-fork-e1697209843997.jpeg\" alt=\"BlackHeart Bike Co. Custom Serakote paint program custom color fork\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/BlackHeart-Bike-Co.-Custom-Serakote-paint-program-custom-color-fork-e1697209843997.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/BlackHeart-Bike-Co.-Custom-Serakote-paint-program-custom-color-fork-e1697209843997-297x170.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/BlackHeart-Bike-Co.-Custom-Serakote-paint-program-custom-color-fork-e1697209843997-800x458.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/BlackHeart-Bike-Co.-Custom-Serakote-paint-program-custom-color-fork-e1697209843997-120x69.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/BlackHeart-Bike-Co.-Custom-Serakote-paint-program-custom-color-fork-e1697209843997-768x440.jpeg 768w\" /></a><figcaption>Photo c. BlackHeart Bike Co. Cerakote color on fork</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2>Custom Paint Pricing</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The pricing seems to be in line with BalckHeart’s ethos of “quality products at a fair price”.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>$300 single-color frame / second color logo</li>\n\n\n\n<li>$100 single-color fork / no logo</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Full custom quote available upon request</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Check out the colors <a href=\"https://www.cerakote.com/shop/cerakote-coating?finishes=cera_h_series\">here</a>. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/BlackHeart-Bike-Co.-Custom-Serakote-paint-program-pink-champagne-e1697210000821.jpeg\"><img src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/BlackHeart-Bike-Co.-Custom-Serakote-paint-program-pink-champagne.jpeg\" alt=\"BlackHeart Bike Co. Custom Serakote paint program pink champagne\" /></a><figcaption>Pink Champagne</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2>Other Paint Options</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>BlackHeart also works with several painters who can deliver anything from BlackHeart past designs, their signature designs, or bring your dream scheme to life. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Painters:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>BlackHeart in house</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Mike Hurley – aka <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/mphpaint/\">MPH Mike</a> – “<em>delivers top-notch paint and can bring any design to life, regardless of the level of detai</em>l”.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Dr. Curtis Bullock – aka <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/savethepostalservice/\">Save The Postal Service</a> – “<em>applies his abstract artwork to create one-of-a-kind designs</em>“.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Check out all of the colors, bikes, and goodies at the link below. </p>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://blackheartbikeco.com/\">BlackHeartBikeCo.com</a></em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/blackheart-bike-co-has-a-new-custom-cerakote-program/\">BlackHeart Bike Co. Has a New Custom Cerakote Program</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Ron Frazelle","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"2895a96b96d971e7c82b09a259a6fb551af141474fcb0a96c4ed1832947161c7","category":"Cycling"}